皮克斯确认《超人总动员 3》并宣布衍生系列《头脑特工队》 https://www.nme.com/news/film/pixar-announce-incredibles-3-and-inside-out-spin-off-series-3782646?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=pixar-announce-incredibles-3-和由内而外的衍生系列Max PilleySat, 10 Aug 2024 19:30:16 +0000 Film NewsNewsDisney+ https://www.nme.com/?p=3782646 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他们还给出了《玩具总动员 5》的上映日期</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/pixar-announce-incredibles-3-and-inside-out-spin-off-series-3782646">皮克斯确认《超人总动员 3》并宣布衍生剧《头脑特工队》</a>将首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上播出。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/incredibles_inside_out-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/pixar">皮克斯</a>确认<i>《超人总动员 3》</i>正在制作中，并宣布推出<i>《头脑特工队》</i>的衍生系列。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="399" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/the-movies-blog/every-pixar-animation-ranked-2539478"><b>每部皮克斯电影按伟大程度排名</b></a></li></ul><p>该动画工作室于周五（8 月 9 日）在迪士尼娱乐展示会上发布了一系列项目公告，并透露已经宣布的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/toy-story-5-confirmed-to-bring-back-woody-buzz-lightyear-3458085"><em>《玩具总动员 5》</em></a>将于 2026 年上映。</p><p> <i>《超人总动员 3》</i>尚未确定确切的上映日期，但据消息称，曾执导前两部电影以及<i>《钢铁巨人》</i>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/the-movies-blog/mission-impossible-ghost-protocol-film-review-781211"><i>《碟中谍 3：幽灵协议》的</i></a>布拉德·伯德也将回归执导《超人总动员 3》的第三部。超级英雄特许经营权。 </p><figure id="attachment_3307667" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3307667" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3307667" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/inside-out-pixar-2015.jpg" alt="由内而外" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/inside-out-pixar-2015.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/inside-out-pixar-2015-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/inside-out-pixar-2015-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/inside-out-pixar-2015-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/inside-out-pixar-2015-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/inside-out-pixar-2015-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3307667" class="wp-caption-text"> 《头脑特工队》图片来源：Pictorial Press Ltd / Alamy Stock Photo</figcaption></figure><p> <i>《头脑特工队》</i>系列——他们的首个此类系列——将被命名为<i>“Dream Productions”</i> ，并将于 2025 年登陆<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney-3">Disney+</a> 。该系列以前两部电影为背景，将探索 Riley 脑海中的工作室，她的梦想实际上是在那里实现的。</p><p> “这是我们的第一个原创系列，我们想做一些独特而大胆的事情，与我们之前所做的任何事情都不同，”皮克斯资深人士皮特·道格特在展示会上说道。</p><p>继最近在影院上映的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/inside-out-2"><i>《头脑特工队 2》</i></a>之后，该电影是 2024 年迄今为止票房最高的电影，也是皮克斯有史以来票房最高的电影，也是有史以来票房第二高的动画电影，仅次于 2019 年版的《头脑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/beyonce-donald-glover-lion-king-prequel-mufasa-trailer-3751842"><i>特工队</i></a>》。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/beyonce-donald-glover-lion-king-prequel-mufasa-trailer-3751842"><i>狮子王</i></a>。</p><p>这部电影与现年 13 岁的莱利重新建立了联系，她在第一部电影中的情绪现在又加入了焦虑、尴尬、嫉妒和倦怠。配音明星包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maya-hawke">玛雅·霍克</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-poehler">艾米·波勒</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tony-hale">托尼·黑尔</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ayo-edebiri">阿约·艾德比</a>里。</p><p>与此同时，2018 年上映的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/incredibles-2-film-review-2353967"><i>《超人总动员 2》</i></a>是皮克斯有史以来利润第二高的电影。当团队试图在平衡家庭生活的同时恢复公众对超级英雄的信心时，这件事发生了。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/incredibles-2-film-review-2353967">在对这部电影的四星评论中</a>， <i>《NME》</i>将其描述为“超级时尚、超级怀旧、适合家庭观看的惊悚片”和“两个小时的欢乐时光”，并补充道：“所以皮克斯的续集不会有任何进展，但如果他们都像这个一样迷人又顽皮，也许没关系？”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/pixar-announce-incredibles-3-and-inside-out-spin-off-series-3782646">皮克斯确认《超人总动员 3》并宣布衍生剧《头脑特工队》</a>将首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上播出。</p> ;
