s://www.nme.com/artists/john-squire">John Squire</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/liam-gallagher-john-squire-tracklist-lyrics-3593699">专辑</a>（46,982 张）。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rod-stewart">罗德·斯图尔特 (Rod Stewart</a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jools-holland">朱尔斯·霍兰德 (Jools Holland)</a>的合作专辑“Swing Fever”销量达到 48,540 张，仅次于斯威夫特位居第二。 </p><figure id="attachment_3509823" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3509823" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3509823" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270.jpg" alt="音乐黑胶唱片收藏复古复古风格 图库照片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3509823" class="wp-caption-text">音乐黑胶唱片收藏复古复古风格 – 图库照片。图片来源：凯莉·鲍登/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>得益于唱片店日和同周发行的《The Tortured Poets Department》，四月份<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-and-record-store-day-see-highest-weekly-vinyl-sales-in-30-years-3752390">黑胶唱片销量创下三十年来最高的每周总销量</a>。<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>官方排行榜公司</em></a>的数据显示，这两场活动共售出 269,134 张黑胶专辑和 37,656 张黑胶单曲，总计 306,791 份。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/physical-music-sales-set-for-first-increase-in-20-years-3775262"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>实体音乐日益流行的消息传出后，有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/number-of-uk-independent-record-shops-hits-10-year-high-3597354">英国独立唱片店数量创 10 年来新高</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-vinyl-sales-2023-reach-highest-level-since-1990-3563676">英国黑胶唱片销量也创 1990 年以来最高水平</a>。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-record-store-opens-in-limerick-3782616">《新唱片店在利默里克开业》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
